@startuml Return_Simple
!theme plain

title Return from Function: Simple Rules

card "Rule 1: Local Variable" #pink {
  **❌ NEVER RETURN**
  
  int* bad() {
    int x = 10;
    return &x;  <-- Dies here!
  }
}

card "Rule 2: Class Member" #lightgreen {
  **✅ SAFE TO RETURN**
  
  class C {
    int data;
    int* get() {
      return &data;  <-- Lives with object
    }
  };
}

card "Rule 3: Static" #lightblue {
  **✅ SAFE TO RETURN**
  
  int* get() {
    static int x = 10;
    return &x;  <-- Lives forever
  }
}

card "Rule 4: Heap" #lightyellow {
  **✅ SAFE (caller deletes)**
  
  int* create() {
    return new int(10);  <-- Lives until delete
  }
}

note bottom
  **Memory Lifetime Rule:**
  Can only return pointer if
  memory lives AFTER function ends!
end note

@enduml